 188:Middlewares/ST/STM32_USB_Host_Library/Core/Src/usbh_ctlreq.c **** /**
 189:Middlewares/ST/STM32_USB_Host_Library/Core/Src/usbh_ctlreq.c ****   * @brief  USBH_GetDescriptor
 190:Middlewares/ST/STM32_USB_Host_Library/Core/Src/usbh_ctlreq.c ****   *         Issues Descriptor command to the device. Once the response received,
 191:Middlewares/ST/STM32_USB_Host_Library/Core/Src/usbh_ctlreq.c ****   *         it parses the descriptor and updates the status.
 192:Middlewares/ST/STM32_USB_Host_Library/Core/Src/usbh_ctlreq.c ****   * @param  phost: Host Handle
 193:Middlewares/ST/STM32_USB_Host_Library/Core/Src/usbh_ctlreq.c ****   * @param  req_type: Descriptor type
 194:Middlewares/ST/STM32_USB_Host_Library/Core/Src/usbh_ctlreq.c ****   * @param  value_idx: Value for the GetDescriptr request
